# Build (Rust)
/target

# Local/CI-only crates.io patch pointing at the sibling erebyx-sdk checkout.
# Must NEVER be committed or packed: the committed Cargo.toml ships a pure
# registry dep so the npm tarball builds from crates.io; this patch only exists
# for in-repo / CI builds against local source (release.yml generates it).
/.cargo

